title: The Football League Show 20.09.2014 webrip X264

SPORT: The Football League Show
On: BBC 1 HD 
Date: Saturday 20th September 2014 
Time: 23:40 to 01:00 

Highlights and analysis from the Football League, presented by Manish Bhasin. Two of the early Championship pacesetters meet as Millwall entertain Nottingham Forest at the Den. Plus extended highlights from Watford's match against Bournemouth and the best of the action from Brighton's clash with struggling Blackpool.
